/api/  - API bindings for client target developer language, like php
/data/ - Directories for indexes with whole Sphinx index files
/etc/  - Sphinx search config templates that used each time when new index created
/log/  - Runtime logs for Sphinx search and other external services
/run/  - Runtime pid files
/usr/  - Some executable or library files that are used by HCE components

schema.xml - default template of Sphinx index data schema
sphinx.template - default template of Sphinx index configuration
